{"tid":1287910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一張 記得攞建制/無政黨區議員傳單","createTime":"2019-07-05T11:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T22:50:51.000Z","uid":90002,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b018e74179d9290954fad72100ea7a8a5cc54fd","tid":1287910,"uid":90002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"頭先行過，發現自己選區個區議員係到派傳單。條友一向都做唔到啲咩，就到選舉個時又出返嚟。點知我見唔少街坊居然攞嚟睇佢啲「政績」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於平時班唔理政治嘅人，隨時因為張傳單就覺得佢地做咗好多嘢投佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因此！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家見到啲建制/偽無政黨候選人放街站嘅時候，不妨攞張支持下佢地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你鐘意攞完之後撕爛佢又得，立即扔咗佢又得。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要見到就要攞！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫佢地攞走張代表用緊佢地選舉經費，又減少咗佢地嘅目標選民，各位街坊鄰居何樂而不為呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終唔係日日都好似琴日天水圍咁有咁多巴絲出到嚟，只能夠小有小做！多有多做！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">踢走保皇黨！</span></span>"},{"pid":"197d1b494b1d362d64c6cc25827f6ef2f866b1b4","tid":1287910,"uid":90002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265e657d6d7d4e58213c08a96fee65c6025e43f4","tid":1287910,"uid":90002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928a9aca548916a1173d553e05fa8b66beee6fb8","tid":1287910,"uid":90002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d85d8c6c86c50405e34b8a3a9d360c40643c57d","tid":1287910,"uid":90002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6385f0f31cccb3f844e00d6d3e65ac60f6176b","tid":1287910,"uid":244318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:50:51.000Z","msg":"幫手拎疊掉垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}